# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# Backward-compat for the old `/subscriptions/[id]` and `/payments/[id]`
# dynamic routes \u2014 we now ship as a static export so these were
# refactored to `/{section}/detail?id=...`. The 200 status code makes
# this a server-side rewrite (URL stays as user typed).

/subscriptions/:id  /subscriptions/detail?id=:id  200
/payments/:id       /payments/detail?id=:id       200
